146-the-future-city-model-p4-s1","ord":0,"text":"\"What about energy?\" Mina asked.","translation_ko":"\"에너지는 어떻게 할까?\" 미나가 물었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-146-the-future-city-model/audio/p4-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"What","charStart":1,"charEnd":5,"startMs":0,"endMs":240},{"word":"about","charStart":6,"charEnd":11,"startMs":240,"endMs":520},{"word":"energy","charStart":12,"charEnd":18,"startMs":520,"endMs":940},{"word":"Mina","charStart":21,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1460,"endMs":1520},{"word":"asked","charStart":26,"charEnd":31,"startMs":1520,"endMs":1960}]},{"id":"daily-146-the-future-city-model-p4-s2","ord":1,"text":"\"Because fossil fuels cause pollution, we should use solar and wind power,\" Jun replied.","translation_ko":"\"화석 연료는 오염을 일으키니까, 태양열이랑 풍력을 써야 해.\" 준이 대답했어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-146-the-future-city-model/audio/p4-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Because","charStart":1,"charEnd":8,"startMs":0,"endMs":540},{"word":"fossil","charStart":9,"charEnd":15,"startMs":540,"endMs":980},{"word":"fuels","charStart":16,"charEnd":21,"startMs":980,"endMs":1300},{"word":"cause","charStart":22,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1300,"endMs":1640},{"word":"pollution","charStart":28,"charEnd":37,"startMs":1640,"endMs":2080},{"word":"we","charStart":39,"charEnd":41,"startMs":2620,"endMs":2620},{"word":"should","charStart":42,"charEnd":48,"startMs":2620,"endMs":2840},{"word":"use","charStart":49,"charEnd":52,"startMs":2840,"endMs":3100},{"word":"solar","charStart":53,"charEnd":58,"startMs":3100,"endMs":3360},{"word":"and","charStart":59,"charEnd":62,"startMs":3360,"endMs":3660},{"word":"wind","charStart":63,"charEnd":67,"startMs":3660,"endMs":3840},{"word":"power","charStart":68,"charEnd":73,"startMs":3840,"endMs":4700},{"word":"Jun","charStart":76,"charEnd":79,"startMs":4700,"endMs":4800},{"word":"replied","charStart":80,"charEnd":87,"startMs":4800,"endMs":5160}]}]},{"id":"daily-146-the-future-city-model-p5","pageNo":5,"spread":"p5","imageUrl":"/seed/daily-146-the-future-city-m